Current rolls come out around 3pm if you want to try that. I show all my friends that visit me in NYC this place!  Jamaican style patties are good too! The Trinidadian style ones come out only on Fridays.  An experience! (I promise they aren't paying me to rave about their bakery! haha)
Absolutely Amazing Food. The doubles, veg Lo main, and the pound cake is my favorite.
Service is fast and excellent, hot and fresh food and bakery products.
Always crowded in the afternoon, they don't take care which sucks but I'll always go as long as they keep making those amazing pastries
They sell the best current rolls in New York City. And everything else I've tried from here has been excellent from their roti to their house special to their meat pie, shrimp wontons ect.
